OL,3,CInquest opens into death of 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in North Yorkshire river
OL,6,FAn inquest has opened into the death
OL,7,Fof a 13-year-old girl who drowned in a
OL,8,Friver near Skipton last month.
OL,10,FPalwasha Akbar, who lived in Bradford,
OL,11,Fdied after getting into difficulties
OL,12,Fin the River Wharfe at Burnsall.
OL,14,FNorthallerton Coroners Court heard
OL,15,Ffrom Assistant North Yorkshire coroner
OL,16,FAlison Norton, who told the court that
OL,17,Fthe provisional cause of Palwasha's
OL,18,Fdeath has been established as drowning.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
