PN,33902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782134325
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in North Yorkshire river
OL,6,FShe said: "Palwasha Akbar was at
OL,7,FBolton Abbey, more specifically
OL,8,FBurnsall, on May 31 2026, when she got
OL,9,Finto some difficulty in the water."
OL,11,FShe was retrieved from the water and
OL,12,Ftaken to Newcastle's Royal Victoria
OL,13,FInfirmary, where she was later
OL,14,Fconfirmed dead.
OL,16,FA day before her 14th birthday,
OL,17,FPalwasha's family previously said that
OL,18,Fthey had gone to the popular riverside
OL,19,Fspot to celebrate her birthday with a
OL,20,Ffamily barbecue.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782134325
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in North Yorkshire river
OL,6,FThe hearing at Northallerton lasted
OL,7,Ffor five minutes and was adjourned to
OL,8,Fa date to be fixed later.
OL,10,FPalwasha's family has previously paid
OL,11,Ftribute, calling her "a bright, kind,
OL,12,Fand caring young girl".
OL,14,FHer family wrote: "Palwasha will be
OL,15,Fremembered for her kindness, her
OL,16,Fbeautiful spirit, her devotion to her
OL,17,Ffriends and family, and the happiness
OL,18,Fshe brought to those around her. Her
OL,19,Flife was taken far too soon, but her
OL,20,Fmemory will live on forever in the
OL,21,Fhearts of everyone who loved her."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
