OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782134325
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in North Yorkshire river
OL,6,FPalwasha was one of 17 people known to
OL,7,Fhave died in open water during a
OL,8,Fperiod of hot weather at the end of
OL,9,FMay, including many from the Calendar
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,12,FMuhammed Secka, 16, died at Rother
OL,13,FValley Country Park; Declan Sawyer,
OL,14,F15, died after an incident at
OL,15,FSwanholme Lakes in Lincolnshire; 13-
OL,16,Fyear-old Reco Puttock died at
OL,17,FLeadbeater Dam in West Yorkshire; 11-
OL,18,Fyear-old Mackenzie Swift died at the
OL,19,FRiver Don in Mexborough and Panashe
OL,20,FMuchenje, 19, died at Balderton Lake
OL,21,Fnear Newark.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
